Seafood good 😋 I like fresh 😋

reviews.text: 海鮮整得好好味😋
星期六(12大人4小朋友)book咗8點,差不多8:15pm齊人起菜,但未食夠1個鐘頭就已經不停比人吹話趕收工。。去流浮山夜晚食海鮮咁多次真係第一次。可能我哋其中有一半海鮮帶嚟加工賺得少又或者其他客已走晒,但都唔應該吹客人囉。重點係book枱時並冇講明話要早收工。而且走時(9:30pm)眼見其他舖都有食客食緊或食完都坐係度吹緊水。佢煮既野味道唔差海鮮同炒飯好味,但趕客態度就扣晒分有待改善~
邦記現正進行翻新大維修，估計今年7、8月重新營業。令人期待！
美味！價錢一般般（即係唔平），環境一般般，所以，四星。
服務貸到不錯，海鮮也煮得很不錯，可以再給他4粒星還有改善空間

reviews.text: Shrimp, razor clam, abalone and scallop are fresh. Well cooked. However, the dont have geoduck like other restaurants in the area. Service is ok.

Tucked away down the long dark alley is a fine seafood restaurant that does not aim to rip off customers but offers a friendly smile and even honest recommendations. Their expertise is preparing seafood using the fresh ingredients sourced directly from the fishermen. If you're a seafood lover looking for an experience you won't forget, this is your spot.
Acceptable price,well cooking skills. Highly recommended .

A very nice place for either lunch or dinner, but needs to well plan the transportation. Food is excellent, we picked our own choice in the seafood store and asked the restaurant to cook for us. The cooking technique is excellent, very delicious, not salty at all, you can really enjoy the freshness and taste of the crab, shrimp,, fish, oyster and bbq pork. I would recommend their oyster, cook fish (not steam), bbq pork, and fish soup, they are exceptionally very good, followed by shrimp and crab. Double thumbs up indeed !
Great food but can be on the pricey side.
